data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Avon Park Lakes. Built in 2005, this corner lot concrete block home comes with a new metal roof and new screened in rear porch. Inside it has an open concept, with the kitchen boasting light colored granite counter tops and white cabinetry, white appliances and an island bringing it all together. Each bedroom is 10x10 or bigger and the single car garage measures 20x13. Being an open concept, the living room is great, has plenty of space to move around and connects you with the rest of the house. Again, corner lot with easy access to Hwy 27 or SR 64!
